(1)

A general view, east from 580 Fifth Ave., at the N.W. corner of 47th Street, showing in the centre No. 444 Madison Ave., (south of 50th St)., and in the background at the left, is the buildings comprising the Rockefeller Institute for Medical Research, (64th north to 67th Sts., and York east to Marie Curie Aves).

June 8, 1932.

P. L. Sperr.

(2)

The same, another view.

June 8, 1932.

P. L. Sperr.

(3)

The same, a year later.

May 15, 1933.

P. L. Sperr.
